      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. So the concrete handles the weight pushing down while the steel handles the tension from bending. You were saying the steel is like the... can you finish that analogy? Also, what happens if the steel starts to rust inside the concrete? Does that mess with the tensile strength bit?",
      "source": "evaluator"
